name: Red Flamingo Cafe LTD
address: 999 Granville St, Vancouver, BC V6Z 2A8, Canada

hasMenuItem.name: Entrées
hasMenuItem.description: Variety of entrées including authentic lahmajun beef, chicken, cheese, beef, spinach, and zaatar pide, plus Romanos small pizza.

hasMenuItem.name: Samosa
hasMenuItem.description: Butter chicken samosa or vegetable option, filled with savory mixtures, served crisp.

hasMenuItem.name: Lentil Soup with Bread
hasMenuItem.description: Smooth lentil soup garnished with fresh cilantro and a sprinkle of paprika, served with two slices of toasted bread.

hasMenuItem.name: Side Order
hasMenuItem.description: Side Choice: Selection includes hummus with bread, guacamole, Tostitos chips in two sizes with salsa, beef nachos, fries with ketchup, and classic nachos.

hasMenuItem.name: Entrées - Sirloin Burger
hasMenuItem.description: With fries.

hasMenuItem.name: All Day Breakfast
hasMenuItem.description: All Day Breakfast selections include avocado on multigrain, ham and cheese on sourdough, and various pides. Options with guacamole, ranch, or chipotle sauces available.

hasMenuItem.name: Flamingo Sandwiches
hasMenuItem.description: Meat club with sourdough, chicken spinach on baguette, or ultimate hummus veggie on multigrain.

hasMenuItem.name: Fresh Salad

hasMenuItem.name: Panini
hasMenuItem.description: Pressed panini with options: Greek veggies on multigrain, spicy capicola, chicken with pesto, or chipotle chicken.

hasMenuItem.description: Create your breakfast with options: select from baguette, sourdough, multigrain, or tortilla. Choose cheese: Swiss, parmesan, mozzarella, cheddar, feta, or vegan. Egg: over easy, sunny-side up, medium, hard.
